{"tid":1660741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動］集思廣益下個星期weekend日程表","createTime":"2019-10-17T16:28:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T05:40:34.000Z","uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"afc8a8df2590a01386dbdc5d43180530c679ab2c","tid":1660741,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:28:42.000Z","msg":"下星期weekend仲未有活動嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時個勢嚟睇NBA同暴雪個勢燒得好旺<br />\n人權法案美國眾議院過咗，但參議院未過<br />\n<br />\n小妹建議可以搞<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反奶共公司遊行</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">暴雪、NBA呢啲唔洗講一定上榜</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但同時要趁機指出Dior、Tiffany、Disney都係奶共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要一視同仁</span></span><br />\n<br />\n至於奶共名人要唔要順便戴佢哋面具幫手宣傳下佢哋就睇大家意願喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終佢哋有fans，怕connect唔成反失效果<br />\n<br />\n不過<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">劉亦菲</span></span>同<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">LeBron James</span></span>呢兩條大仆街我就覺得要強力宣傳嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n次選就蝗嘉爾呢件China Man啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">參議院方面可以參考翻上次集會形式</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不過揮美國旗方面有多啲人參與會更好<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">同埋人數一定要多過上次</span><br />\n<br />\n小小建議，希望大家多多交流留comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋請幫P牌仔推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />重要post唔想沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />難得而家可以食住個國際勢，機不可失"},{"pid":"e1ea325a648413c84de41dca3fa7432aaf74fa03","tid":1660741,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:29:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwJzHzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwJzHzo.jpg&h=eb217258&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"92d57f09a02e1183a5a916d650b4221dbfc54db5","tid":1660741,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:29:25.000Z","msg":"無力都推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f945a930d1eab4c95feaf5ab6a22f4a9e358dc7","tid":1660741,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"劉亦菲個仆街撐警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />頂佢個肺"},{"pid":"57ee1717c1ce1151e895cf51c8cd5f4d24ff3a2c","tid":1660741,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:30:25.000Z","msg":"幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5039cd7ee81fc5341ec6487cc6c249f41469662b","tid":1660741,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:31:03.000Z","msg":"有人幫手推未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810b5f67c46f853ce18ccbb58396735b4136f3a8","tid":1660741,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bfcbf07756d1080c422d097d078568a9d1bcf17","tid":1660741,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T16:45:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" cla